description:
Latest on the Dems' filibuster failure in Senate. Joy Behar is an idiot. Scary poll numbers: Dems want to put unvaxxed in camps, take their children (including Clay's), ban anti-vaccine speech. Even CNN disappointed in Biden. Senator Marsha Blackburn joins Clay and Buck to discuss the Dem filibuster fail, China, the border. GOP should run on crime, inflation, and immigration in 2022. Gorsuch and Sotomayor deny NPR mask story and claim they are "warm colleagues and friends."
